column8: Two DAP representatives have condemned a Facebook post made against Minister in the Prime Minister’s Department Azalina Othman as “a disgrace to female dignity”The post, which was made by Facebook user Otai BERSIH last Thursday, showed a picture of Azalina with the caption “Tiada seorang pun sanggup nak rogol saya.” (No one is willing to rape me).We should not be making personal attacks, especially ones which so blatantly violate female dignity,” she told FMT. “There’s always a boundary in our public space.”Sos tomato
